Sentencas: A low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell system was developed to use bioethanol and glycerol as fuels directly.
Titulo: Direct biofuel low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This system achieved a maximum power density of 215 mW cm(-2) by using glycerol at 580 degrees C and produced a great impact on sustainable energy and the environment.
Titulo: Direct biofuel low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
